{"id":"20260308-001","filename":"20260308-001-api-design.md","relativePath":"backend/20260308-001-api-design.md","frontmatter":{"id":"20260308-001","title":"RESTful API design guidelines","date":"2026-03-08T00:00:00.000Z","sprint":"sprint1","category":"architecture","deciders":["Bob","Charlie"],"status":"accepted","summary":"Established REST API conventions including versioning, error format, and pagination"},"html":"<h1>RESTful API design guidelines</h1>\n<h2>Background</h2>\n<p>Need consistent API design patterns across all endpoints.</p>\n<h2>Conventions</h2>\n<h3>Versioning</h3>\n<p>All endpoints prefixed with <code>/api/v1/</code>.</p>\n<h3>Error format</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-json\"><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"error\"</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"code\"</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"VALIDATION_ERROR\"</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"message\"</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Email is required\"</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"details\"</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"field\"</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"email\"</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">\"reason\"</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"required\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h3>Pagination</h3>\n<p>Cursor-based pagination with <code>?cursor=xxx&#x26;limit=20</code>. Response includes <code>nextCursor</code>.</p>"}